SELUDLULISELWE emaphoyiseni udaba lokhulumela i-ANC kuzwelonke uMnuz Pule Mabe osolwa ngokuhlukumeza ngokocansi omunye wabasebenzi baseLuthuli House, okuyikomkhulu lenhlangano. UNksz Kgoareno Kekana uthi ngeke alale engendlalelwe lolu daba, lusaya kude kuze kufike lapho azoneliseka khona ngobulungiswa. Uthe uselivulile icala emaphoyiseni walufaka naseCCMA udaba. Uthe uphoxekile ngendlela i-ANC esingathe ngayo udaba, wathi ubona sengathi kube nokwenzelela. Ukhale ngokuthi indlela obekubizwa ngayo ofakazi ibimcindezela. USihlalo wesigungu ebesisingethe udaba ku-ANC, uMnuz Sdumo Dlamini, uthe bagculisekile ukuthi udaba luphathwe ngendlela kodwa engalwedlulisela phambili ummangali uma engenelisekile. Kuvele nokuthi i-ANC yenze izincomo zokuthi kuchitshiyelwe imigomo yayo yangaphakathi ebhekene nokunukubezwa ngokocansi bagcizelela nokuthi ummangali aqhubeke nokusebenza eLuthuli House.